in a completely different way.

00:03:10.410 --> 00:03:15.690
I mean, you have cultures where getting purple
Uggs is the way you please and if you buy

00:03:15.690 --> 00:03:20.250
that perfect pair of purple Uggs, you will
be accepted by the tribe and you won't be

00:03:20.250 --> 00:03:24.260
alienated and outside and if you don't buy
