00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:45.020
And that was kind of the basis of the book.

00:04:45.020 --> 00:04:48.840
And I think the other thing that I've seen,
and certainly know myself as a teenage girl,

00:04:48.840 --> 00:04:55.250
because I really do feel I'm about 15 even
though I'm dressed in this body and I look

00:04:55.250 --> 00:04:56.250
