00:05:16.449 --> 00:05:24.069
weepy, you're too sensitive. You take things
too seriously."

00:05:24.069 --> 00:05:27.800
And I think for boys, it gets cut off at a
much earlier point.

00:05:27.800 --> 00:05:31.499
But I think for girls, they're allowed to
go a little longer.

00:05:31.499 --> 00:05:36.510
And then they begin to feel bad about their
level of passion and their level of intensity

00:05:36.510 --> 00:05:37.520
